{"tid":1362980,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[726]  機場之不合作遊車河","createTime":"2019-07-25T04:42:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T04:48:34.000Z","uid":255007,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"504ade318d24688cf669a948c18a2400019e0b48","tid":1362980,"uid":255007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T04:42:23.000Z","msg":"有無人發覺，機場快綫個港鐵站點解無閘機既？<br />\n<br />\n其實係因為想方便旅客/使用者，拖住行李機場唔洗俾d閘機kick住<br />\n<br />\n而背後就衍生出一個bug<br />\n<br />\n當大家黎到機場夢遊時，但又想一覽機場快綫既風采，其實唔洗錢都可以做到，可以全日享受24分鐘到達市區又或者到達機場既快感<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">只要大家想遊車河既時候，係機場站上車<br />\n然後坐定定到香港站，但千祈唔好太舒服而訓著<br />\n如果唔係既話就會原車折返機場，會再浪費多24分鐘再去香港站嫁啦，時間咁就晒左嫁啦</span><br />\n<br />\n而機場快綫列車既座位大概有500個左右<br />\n最後希望大家都可以坐定定咁暢遊機場快綫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd23fe10409e746a38059a3b3b3a887c6ab24f13","tid":1362980,"uid":255007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T04:43:47.000Z","msg":"推一下"},{"pid":"f98ca1fb2fa202fb808cf96efbc3952686b03507","tid":1362980,"uid":255007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T04:44:09.000Z","msg":"推兩下"},{"pid":"b5a891ee8a95856fdd0f8faf48e108e9cb861f96","tid":1362980,"uid":255007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T04:44:19.000Z","msg":"推三下"},{"pid":"7a0d7aaac6adcf678ec06115370f50f0a1eeed7a","tid":1362980,"uid":38482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T04:45:56.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n武力要升級 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">文宣都要升級</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">登報高峰期盡做</span></span><br />\n(呼籲!!)(汲取G20經驗)關於登報一事提升輿論問題<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1360136\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">